record.title: MEASURE PLACED ON THE CALENDAR--S. 761

speaking.paragraph: Mr. President, it is my understanding that S. 761 is at the desk and due for a second reading.

record.chair: The clerk will read the title of the bill for the second time.
record.narrative: The legislative clerk read as follows:

speaking.paragraph: Mr. President, I object to any further proceedings on this piece of legislation.

record.chair: Objection is heard. The bill will be placed on the calendar.
